            <Abstract ID="Abs1" Language="En">
              <Heading>Abstract</Heading>
              <Para>A method is reported which allows the operation of optically pumped farinfrared (FIR) gas lasers in a simple way: A spectrophone is used to control and to stabilize the pump laser frequency in order to achieve most efficient optical pumping of the FIR laser gas.</Para>
            </Abstract>
